title: Valentine Panic
description: You need a job and fast. However, every job to apply for seems to not have any positions available to you. Before you give up, you find luck in the Pink Lady Cafe, working a full-time job for Valentine's Day. Simple, right?Features:4 Romance Options (2 Male, 2 Female)Genderless and Nameable Main CharacterFull Voice ActingMemory Card Game! (Plus Endless Mode, a high-paced time-consumer!)A couple of hidden Easter Eggs?Team:Writer/Producer - Michaela LawsArtists - ReddArt, AnirhapsodistEditor
